    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 35 min, remove the dish[es] from the oven and pour the <strong>herby stock</strong> all over the potatoes and tomatoes</p><p>Squeeze over the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> and top the chicken with the <strong>reserved lemon slices</strong></p>",
