    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the dish[es] to the oven for 15-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>baked lemon & herb chicken with cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
