    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, add a few knobs of <strong>butter</strong> to the potatoes and leave to melt</p><p>Tear your<strong> parsley</strong> and<strong> dill </strong>all over the <strong>baked lemon & herb chicken with cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>with some<strong> olive oil </strong>and serve it alongside</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
